        <div class="body">
            <p>It means, that input string is not in current locale. In this case iconv can't converts all symbols correctly .</p>

<p>You should change current locale or convert string to ascii beforeadding it to the document. Like it described here - <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.search.charset.html">http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/â€¦</a>:
$docText = iconv('ISO-8859-1', 'ASCII//TRANSLIT', $docText);</p>

